snippet.title: 9-Bit Armies: A Bit Too Far - Nextfest Livestream with the Devs
snippet.description:
Lead Game Designer (Biffy) and Community Manager (Schism Navigator) take on the community in a variety of Team vs. Team and Player vs. Player battles in our latest RTS release!

Wishlist on Steam here:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1439750/9Bit_Armies_A_Bit_Too_Far/
